@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy - Zariya";
}
<section class="py-5 text-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF5F5 0%, #FFF0F0 100%);">
    <div class="container py-4">
        <span class="badge bg-danger mb-3 px-3 py-2 text-uppercase" style="border-radius: 30px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.75rem;">Legal & Compliance</span>
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-dark mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="lead text-muted mx-auto" style="max-width: 600px; font-size: 1.1rem;">
            Your privacy is of utmost importance. Learn how Zariya protects, manages, and uses your personal and medical information.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
<div class="container py-5" style="max-width: 900px;">
    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm p-5" style="border-radius: 20px;">

        <div class="alert alert-info mb-5 d-flex gap-3 align-items-start" style="border-radius: 12px;">
            <i class="fas fa-info-circle fa-lg mt-1 text-info"></i>
            <div>
                <strong>GDPR & NDPR Compliance Statement:</strong> Zariya operates under strict principles of data minimization and consent. We collect only what is essential to locate a matching blood donor and save a life.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 fw-bold text-danger mb-3"><i class="fas fa-database me-2"></i>1. Detailed Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">In order to provide our real-time matching service, we collect and process several categories of information:</p>
            <div class="table-responsive mb-3">
                <table class="table table-bordered table-striped" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">
                    <thead class="table-light">
                        <tr>
                            <th>Category</th>
                            <th>Data Collected</th>
                            <th>Purpose</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Identity Data</strong></td>
                            <td>Full name, CNIC number, date of birth, gender.</td>
                            <td>Identity verification, prevention of fraudulent accounts.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Contact Data</strong></td>
                            <td>Phone number, email address.</td>
                            <td>Direct communication between accepted donors and recipients.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Health & Medical</strong></td>
                            <td>Blood group, last donation date, medical condition, donation type.</td>
                            <td>Determining eligibility and matching compatibility.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Geographical</strong></td>
                            <td>City, province.</td>
                            <td>Filtering searches to match local donors with regional needs.</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 fw-bold text-danger mb-3"><i class="fas fa-handshake me-2"></i>2. Explicit Consent & Control</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">By registering on Zariya, you explicitly consent to the following:</p>
            <ul class="text-muted" style="line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Your name, blood group, city, and bio will be visible in the public search directory.</li>
                <li>Your phone number and email address are hidden by default from unauthenticated visitors.</li>
                <li>When a recipient is logged in and sends a blood request to a donor, the donor can view the recipient's name and details.</li>
                <li>Once the donor accepts the request, contact information is exchanged for direct coordination.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 fw-bold text-danger mb-3"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-2"></i>3. Comprehensive Security Protocols</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">We have implemented advanced technical security controls to protect your data:</p>
            <ul class="text-muted" style="line-height: 1.8;">
                <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> All database communication is encrypted in transit and passwords are hashed.</li>
                <li><strong>Access Control:</strong> System administrators have restricted role-based access.</li>
                <li><strong>Session Expiry:</strong> Active sessions expire after 8 hours of inactivity to prevent unauthorized access on shared devices.</li>
                <li><strong>Anti-Scraping:</strong> Search directories are limited to authenticated or restricted queries to prevent bulk data harvesting of donor phone numbers.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 fw-bold text-danger mb-3"><i class="fas fa-history me-2"></i>4. Data Retention & Permanent Deletion</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">How long we retain your data and how you can manage it:</p>
            <p class="text-muted" style="line-height: 1.8;">
                We retain your information as long as your account is active. If you choose to delete your account, your profile, contact details, donor listings, and medical logs are permanently purged from our database immediately. Transaction histories (like logs of past fulfilled donations) are anonymized for aggregate statistics.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h2 class="h4 fw-bold text-danger mb-3"><i class="fas fa-phone-alt me-2"></i>5. Contacts & Data Protection Officer</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">If you have any questions, privacy concerns, or wish to request a copy of your data, please reach out to our Data Protection Officer:</p>
            <p class="text-muted">
                <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@zariya.org" class="text-danger fw-bold">privacy@zariya.org</a><br />
                <strong>Address:</strong> Zariya Digital Donor Portal Office, Lahore, Punjab, Pakistan.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>